520
00:38:47,180 --> 00:38:48,740
Morning.

521
00:38:53,300 --> 00:38:54,960
Morning!

522
00:39:03,100 --> 00:39:04,830
You're up?

523
00:39:05,670 --> 00:39:07,280
Do you still have a fever?

524
00:39:07,280 --> 00:39:09,730
