527
00:39:15,010 --> 00:39:17,780
Today is her birthday!

528
00:39:17,780 --> 00:39:19,840
So what? What does it have to do with me?

529
00:39:19,840 --> 00:39:23,750
Did you forget or have you never even remembered?

530
00:39:24,400 --> 00:39:27,190
She never even told me.

531
